HEADWORD: lastingness
<hw>lastingness</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>permanence by virtue of the
power to resist stress or force.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> durability, enduringness, strength.</syn>⟦br⟧
